				<section xml:id="sec-pwc-irv">
					
					<title>Pairwise Comparisons and Instant Runoff Voting</title>
					
					<assemblage>
						<title>Motivating Questions</title>
						<p>
							<statement>
								In this section, we will explore the following questions.
