									<li>What is instant runoff voting? What are its strengths and weaknesses?</li>				<li>What does Arrow's Theorem say, and what are its consequences for democracy?</li>	  				
								</ol>
							</statement>
						</p>
					</assemblage>
					
					<subsection xml:id="subsec-pwc">
